race.comment: OFFA'S DYKE (7) improved sharply second-up when closing off into the placings here. Looks to be hitting his straps now and should relish the rise in trip. With Milnes booked, confidence is boosted. POWER PRIMO (10) was sound resuming into fourth here two weeks ago. Better suited stepping out over this journey, though she will likely get back from the draw. Expect her to be charging late. WRATH (4) has mixed his form but his peaks measure up. Gets in well with the 3kg claimer engaged. Don't dismiss in this thin contest. GIFTERA (9) was sent back to the trials after a wayward barrier jump at Clare. Drawn sticky but worth keeping safe.
